The evidence with the title 'Obama criminalize free speech? - FactCheck.org ' says May 7, 2012  ... Q : did president Obama secretly sign a law that makes it a crime to protest against him or ask him a question he doesn't like? A: no. He openly announced the signing of a bill overwhelmingly passed by Congress that slightly revises a 1971 law against trespassing into areas under Secret Service protection  ... 
